## 10. Feature: All Records (Invoice List)

### Record Cards

Each invoice/bill is rendered as a card (not a row in a table on mobile). Cards show:
- Invoice number and date
- Party name
- Total amount
- Outstanding balance (invoice total minus all payments allocated to this party via FIFO)
- Payment status badge: Paid / Partial / Outstanding
- Due date status: Overdue Xd / Due today / Due in Xd (only when the party has credit days set)
