When the user clicks an overdue or recent-activity panel on the dashboard and is redirected to Records, the date range filters are pre-populated to match the dashboard's selected range. This is the `drillRecords()` function.

### Undo Toast

Deletion of a record shows a 5-second undo toast. The deleted record is first saved to `almadhi/trash/record_ID`, then removed from the real path. The undo button restores it from the backup and removes the trash copy.

