- `431px – 900px` — tablet portrait: topbar inline nav, no sidebar
- `≥ 901px` — desktop: persistent sidebar, full topbar

### Samsung Galaxy Z Fold Inner Screen

The app has a specific nav for foldable phones when the inner 8" display is active (`#inner-pill-nav`). On this display size, the page is wide enough for a topbar nav but not quite a full sidebar. The inner pill nav shows at the top with icon+label buttons.

### Topbar Height CSS Variable

```css
:root { --topbar-h: 52px; }
